/ (root)
├─ index.html           → Home
│   Hero section: Name & tagline
│   Brief overview of services/expertise
│   CTA buttons: “View Services” → /services, “Contact Me” → /contact
│
├─ services/            → Services
│   Technical & Automation, QA & Functional Testing, Project & Operations Management
│
├─ core-skills/         → Core Skills
│   CRM & Automation, Project Management, QA & Testing, Web & System Support
│
├─ portfolio/           → Portfolio / Projects
│   Showcase technical projects, CRM setups, workflow automation, QA results
│
├─ testimonials/        → Testimonials
│   Client reviews, success stories, measurable results
│
├─ contact/             → Contact
│   Inquiry form, email & social links, optional CTA to Little Things brand → /littlethings
│
├─ about/               → About
│   Bio & professional story
│   Mission & approach
│   Highlights of expertise
│   Optional personal touch: photo, quote
│   Philosophical Core: guiding principles, work philosophy, creative & technical values
│
├─ careers/             → Freelance / Career Opportunities
│   Entry-Level & Mid-Level roles
│
├─ target-clients/      → Target Clients
│   Startups/SMEs, companies needing CRM/workflow solutions
│
├─ footer/              → Footer
│   Quick links to all pages, copyright info, social media/GitHub links
│
└─ .nojekyll            → Disables GitHub Pages Jekyll processing
